Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurai, we'll be taking a family trip\Nto a hot spring over Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have that time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not take advantage of all those\Npublic holidays and go somewhere yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she suggested, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been playing video games\Nfor 72 hours straight since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so this is the last of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That unnecessary rhythmic flourish...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}knew {\i0}it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:11.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uzaki-{\i1}chan {\i0}Wants to Hang Out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:32.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Episode 4: I Want to Hang Out\NTogether Over the Holiday!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free today?\NI mean, you totally are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This popping over unannounced is a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're off work, and I figured\Na loner like you would be home gaming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So instead I stopped by to hang out\Nwith you, my senior and my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great news, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock off that weirdly\Nsuperior tone--it's infuriating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play Doramon Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:02:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's still a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big spawning event during Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's catch 'em all--together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the app.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buuut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was too embarrassed to play alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Man, I can read you like a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you turn it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a major drag.\NThen again, it {\i1}is {\i0}a holiday week...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to die of boredom,\Nso sure--count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a Lousy Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one thing to be all scowly,\Nbut walking around with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's gonna report you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop backing away like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you sure are catching a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:12.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gorilla"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all Gorillas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They keep popping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, my eyes hurt. Can't look at the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Then let's go buy you some glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy running into you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So your eyes hurt\Nfrom playing games too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up,\Nhe'll be Doramon Go-ing to lockup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give {\i1}you {\i0}"lockup."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you played games the entire time\Nwe were at the hot spring, Sakurai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he'd probably {\i1}still {\i0}be holed up\Nplaying games if {\i1}I {\i0}hadn't come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's here and all, why don't\Nyou ask Ami to be your glassistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My glassistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the loner indoorsman\Ngame-addict here needs those things:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Protect Your Eyes from Blue Light!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Computer glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the ones that cut down\Non blue light from LCD displays.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are supposed to keep\Nyour eyes from getting tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted a pair myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. Might be good for long gaming sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! The lenses are a faint yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're like thin sunglasses, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in glasses, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nice! Should we try some others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, which ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:48.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,How about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm some kind of toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are {\i1}perfect{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! They hide your glare-mug\Nso you look like a normal person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who says I have a glare-mug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably wear\Nthose at work and school, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you find {\i1}those{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do {\i1}you {\i0}have to play around with me, too, Ami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow, that is too much. Can I take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look this way... no, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep laughing... my phone's shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try, uh, try these on next, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're laughing already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They work with your natural fierce expression\Nto make you look like a mafioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you'd assassinate someone\Nwith a long piece of wire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or like you're dominating\Nsome criminal underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw on a white coat,\Nand you could be a mad scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do {\i1}not{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shelf were these on? I'm putting them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once, Senpai--just one time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brush your hair back with\Nthose little round glasses on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll turn into an\Nembarrassingly tropey character!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it you {\i1}want {\i0}from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry! Try this last pair on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These were a serious choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now make a fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your mouth a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayyyyy-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, that was funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better pick out\Nyour own glasses there, Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, which ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,These are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do like a pink frame...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's gotta be red!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out, Sakurai.\NDoesn't Hana look good in glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look dumber, strangely enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Strangely enough"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was complimenting you earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you called me a mafioso!\NThat makes it a wash, you big dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Picky, picky!\NThat's what you are--you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're {\i0}the one who has to\Nwatch what she says and does!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\i1}you're {\i0}the one who's always angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You asked for it, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a moron calls someone a moron, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said it yourself, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you said it first, moron! Moron! Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. They're always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed out on getting glasses,\Nand it's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Got a Lousy Cat Dandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\i0}just {\i1}had {\i0}to start something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another Gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't dump the blame on me\Njust 'cause you're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's power harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I got a Lousy Cat Genius this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly it's {\i1}your {\i0}fault, because {\i1}you {\i0}started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but Gorillas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, {\i1}your {\i0}problem is--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechst Station. Nechst Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lot of people getting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with this game, the more people\Naround you, the higher the monster spawn rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? A Lousy Cat Cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still Gorillas here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much do you like gorillas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't. {\i1}They {\i0}like {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as we get where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andenechst Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andefallo-Wing Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's crazy crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right--there's a soccer match\Nat a nearby stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, huh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something incredibly soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Can't really help it in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad--and at this rate,\Nit'll get {\i1}really {\i0}bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't budge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I just going to have to grin and bear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of something else\Nand pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's n-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's {\i1}that {\i0}doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta get my mind on something else, pronto...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:15.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"When Your Chest's Tight and\NYour Heart Won't Stop Pounding"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am {\i1}fine{\i0}. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are traps everywhere I turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see nothing. I hear nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I turn my consciousness inward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?\NHe got so quiet all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh--his eyelashes are really long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His face is {\i1}so close{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Picture it--now! A clear blue sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like one of those\Nwall-pound things, huh? Ha ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vast field, stretching\Nas far as the eye can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your arm tired? Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal-clear, unclouded water,\Nits surface like a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this. I can make it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my eyes closed and my ears dulled,\Nmy other senses are heighten--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, uh, Senpai... Thanks for earli--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he out cold--on his feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door is closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This is our stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai? Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait--what time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.78,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Received Calls"\N"Uzaki\NUzaki\NUzaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a ton of calls from Uzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}that's {\i0}what happened during...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...during Golden Week?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I blacked out before it got to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If {\i1}she {\i0}made me feel that way,\NI figured I'd be better off unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, can he just turn his\Nconsciousness off and on at will?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he, a ninja? Spooky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're young--you should be more carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm sure my Ami\Nis hanging out with boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think something so hilar--er,\Nterrible happened to you afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to say "hilarious"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow up with Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she's the one who invited you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on,\Nbut I'm not going to engage. Too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's {\i0}engaging {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking at the calendar when it hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no holidays in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}that's {\i0}why you're so down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got weekends off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the more and longer breaks\Nthe better, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greedy much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A three-day break really winds you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I get depressed thinking\Nabout this weather sticking around
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for another month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. But after the rainy\Nseason comes summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not before exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about next weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't startle me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You {\i0}startled {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This same old loner of a senior,\Nsuggesting we go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell must be frozen over! Completely frozen over!\NAnd now I know why it's raining!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because {\i1}you {\i0}say such weird stuff! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make heads or tails\Nof this mixed-up conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't work for you, then never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... is there someplace you had in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know: How about an outing by train?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, your face is all red.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. No trains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you mind if I just\Nthrow something together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one frightening laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's not every day that {\i1}you {\i0}invite {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, I felt bad for what\Nhappened over Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I told Ami,\Nshe said I should follow up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You totally are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, if I were mad, it'd be a big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pouring. Forget going out in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's still home...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Super Huge"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured if it was gonna rain anyway,\NI may as well play games at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd cook, so I did a little shopping,\Nand it started raining harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I left the supermarket,\Nit was a total disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the sentiment,\Nbut don't go overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I borrow your shower?\NOh... and a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I shouldn't have worn my favorite shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I'm soaked clear through to my undies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! TMI!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shirt is {\i1}ginormous{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just get lunch started\Nbefore we start playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any good cookware,\Nso I'm giving you my old pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredibly nice of you. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uza Curry" "Beef"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no cook. How about washing these veggies?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully obedient today, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that everything's been\Ngoing wrong for you today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine--I'm a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you couldn't taste the porridge\NI made for you when you were sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there's a little score-settling in the mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cooking will have your\Nunsophisticated palate {\i1}moaning{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, you've gone a step too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What game do you want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You downloaded Meowcraft! Let's play that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together to build\Nsomething totally out-there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too perfect a way for\Na college student to waste a day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to be a useless college student?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've been one all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew! That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was asking too much\Nto finish our build in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}did {\i0}get torn down a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just work on it\Nthe next time you're over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The... next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the scary laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the curry pot in\Nthe fridge just like that, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll taste even better after sitting overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've heard that. Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it sit overnight and the roux\Nsoaks into the meat and veggies,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which release their umami components--amino\Nacids, sugars--into the roux!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you get a richer\Numami flavor all through the curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though today's was already plenty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "the next time"... How about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to pick up where we left off today?\NSure. God knows I'm free.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's hang out again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... wait--what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:22:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I seem to have\Nleft my pass at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}so {\i0}disorganized.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:44.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Episode 5: I Want to Meddle \Nin My Friend`s Business!"